attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure III
Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Treasure II

data.description: One Owner home in a very desirable neighborhood with NO HOA.  Close to shopping, schools, restaurants and beautiful downtown Swansboro and minutes to Emerald Isle and the beach!   Low maintenance LVP and Tile Flooring throughout the entire house.  The baths and kitchen have been remodeled and upgraded with high end fixtures and appliances.  The kitchen is outfitted with a new Frigidaire Gallery Range, Maytag Microwave with Air Fryer Capability, Bosch Dishwasher and a Whirlpool Refrigerator with Dual Ice Compartments.   A Wired 20KW Kohler Generator with 200 amp service is also included.  As you enter the foyer you will see a stairway on the left to the 4 Bedrooms upstairs and a Den/Office on your right.  Continuing on through the foyer leads to the Family Room/Breakfast Area and Kitchen with the Formal Dining Room off the Kitchen to your right.  Passing through the double doors to the huge Trex covered deck leads to the custom Hardscape with seating area, firepit, low voltage LED lighting and beautiful landscaping.  Within the fenced in yard there is a Heartland 10x12 shed for tools and projects and even a Greenhouse.  The Chicken Coop and even the chickens can remain if interested!  Come see this awesome home soon!  Restricted hours due to work schedules.  See remarks.
